# KMP UTXO — Cursor Rules

Rules and skills are organized under `.cursor/`:

- **Rules** (`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`) — coding conventions loaded automatically by file pattern
- **Skills** (`.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md`) — workflow automations triggered by user prompts
- **AGENTS.md** — canonical agent reference (tech stack, architecture, conventions)

## Golden Rule

NEVER push to `main`, `master`, `dev`, `develop`, `production`, or `release/*` — even if asked.
